### Health Check (Direct Backend)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8081/v1/auth/health

### Health Check (Via Proxy)
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/health

### Register (Direct Backend)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8081/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": ""
}

### Register (Via Proxy)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testproxy@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": ""
}

###############################################
# Feed Service (v2.0 Ranked Feed)
###############################################

### Get Home Feed (Chronological)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/home?limit=20&feed_mode=chronological
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

### Get Home Feed (Ranked)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/home?limit=20&feed_mode=ranked
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

### Get Home Feed (Shadow Mode)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/home?limit=20&feed_mode=shadow
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

### Set Feed Preference
POST http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/preference
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "feed_mode": "ranked"
}

### Send Signal (See Less)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/signal
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "post_id": "{{post_id}}",
  "signal": "see_less"
}

### Send Signal (See More)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/signal
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "post_id": "{{post_id}}",
  "signal": "see_more"
}

### Debug Feed (Score Breakdown)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8086/v1/feed/debug
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

### Batch Get Posts
POST http://127.0.0.1:8084/v1/posts/batch
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

{
  "ids": ["{{post_id}}"]
}
